This directory contains code specific to SCFT calculations.

Subdirectories:

bdstep/        -
mcmove/        -
compressor/    - 
analyzer/      -
perturbation/  -
ramp/          -
trajectory/    -

C++ Files:

Simulator.h    - Simulator<D> class template header (main object)
Simulator.tpp  - Simulator<D> class template definition
Simulator.cpp  - Simulator<D> explicit instantiations for D=1,2,3
SimState.h     - SimState<D> class template header (main object)
SimState.tpp   - SimState<D> class template definition
SimState.cpp   - SimState<D> explicit instantiations for D=1,2,3

Makefile and makefile fragments:

sources.mk    - list of source files (makefile fragment)
makefile      - main makefile for rpc/fts directory tree

Doxygen documentation files:

fts.mod       - defintion of the Rpc_Scft doxygen module

